7:T54b,Tracy is soul guide and mentor, energetic interpreter, and international facilitator based on the Kohala Coast. She is given to empowering souls deeply landed in matter and honoring the multitude of realities and expressions of love within each of us. Tracy has spent the last decade immersed in both study and practice within traditions of healing and integration, energetic mastery, and soul initiation. She combines lived experience, years of training and depth of study with intuitive adeptness and precise energetic attunement in her work. 

Tracy's soul mentorship is focused on midwifing souls into embodied depth and well being.  Her one on one practice welcomes individuals and couples and covers the following:
-Emotional fluency
-Nervous system regulation and stabilization
-Neuroplasticity training
-Relational wellness
-Erotic embodiment
-Practical integration for soulful living
-Clearing patterns and behaviors that inhibit wellness and radiance

Tracy's group work focuses on supporting fields of vibratory coherence between humans and building group capacity for generative healing , creativity, and collaboration. This work is deeply supportive for organizations, collectives, and any group wanting to understand relational dynamics to support generative and resourcing environments. Reach out directly to find out more about group work.3:["$","$L6",null,{"islandSlug":"big-island","islandDisplayName":"Big Island","modalitySlug":"energy-healing","modalityName":"Energy Healing","practitioners":[{"id":"571713e3-949d-4eee-93fa-208c3559b7fb","name":"Alice Tobin","businessName":"Alice Tobin Painfree Solutions","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/52012b6ae4b0c874e504d0e3/t/5326457ce4b09aa77d05a723/1395017085855/AliceTobinLogo+painfree.jpg?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Energy Healing","modalities":["Energy Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"Holistic healing with Eden's Energy Medicine by Alice Tobin. Workshops, classes and individual healing sessions on Hilton Head Island SC.","location":"Captain Cook","rating":5,"lat":19.4727,"lng":-155.918052,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","verified":false},{"id":"4aa59f98-6315-4e4f-ae20-a8ca64a5c54b","name":"Brittany Clair Farmer","businessName":"Energetic Healing Hawaii","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/624dfee0c055b72569f14a74/t/6324efc7a98add43bac3a7bd/1663365067602/public.jpeg?format=1500w","type":"practitioner","modality":"Energy Healing","modalities":["Energy Healing"],"sessionType":"in_person","acceptsNewClients":true,"bio":"We create safe and transformative experiences through the use of Sacred Ceremonial Cacao and multi layered Sound Healing. Private offerings available.","location":"Holualoa","rating":5,"lat":0,"lng":0,"tier":"free","externalBookingUrl":"","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","